>Talon:
> 
>"One is POW, the other one is missing in this base"said 
>Talon while she tought only for her in a sacartic way "and a former one 
>helping in the hunt"

"Acknowledged" Legacy intoned thoughtfully as he examined is own internal records of these events. Many of these things were new, and he found them eminently fascinating. As this time line stretched away from what he knew, it was comforting know that now there was a chance for survival for the future. 

He glanced at Talon, well aware of her origins from the data given him from the future. However he remained silent on that matter. If she was choosing to hold the secret, so would he. 

>Talosn started to type in a computer that had conections 
>in all the base, she was checking all the terminals and she suddely said by com 
>link"Lord Perseus, some one has been here before... A Predacon... He downloaded 
>a pod's information to the BlackFortress. .. Acording to records it was a time a 
>go among Jiaxus's attack and today... what this could mean?"

Legacy was about to respond and give assistance when his own sensors discovered something. "I am detecting minion transmissions. One from somewhere inside the base, but another originating from somewhere much further away. I am attempting to locate now."

OOC: You can assume legacy that Legacy is both boosting and encrypting Maximal/Autobot com signals. 

Preston
(Legacy)
